   <text>
      <body>
        <div>
            <pb facs="#TL-0471.jpg" n="part3_p079.jpg" xml:id="img_0079" corresp="https://id.acdh.oeaw.ac.at/tillich-lectures/part3_p079.jpg"/>
            
            <p facs="#facs_79_tr_3">
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_3_tl_1" n="N001"/>- 466-
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_3_tl_2" n="N002"/>is the way in which the S[n]lightenment comes, but it CAN come from another INNER-regious way.
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_3_tl_3" n="N003"/>And all this I try to give you in these lectures and others, in theology generally, is to prepare those
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_3_tl_4" n="N004"/>who are able to understand the real meaning of the Christian symbols so that they are able to give
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_3_tl_5" n="N005"/>[fine?
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_3_tl_6" n="N006"/>the transition in a very referred, feeling-in, empathetic way.
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_3_tl_7" n="N007"/>This leads to a second principle, to which I want to come, namely the principle of
            </p>
            <p facs="#facs_79_tr_2">
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_2_tl_1" n="N001"/>question and answer, which is the method of religious education. I have often been asked: what
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_2_tl_2" n="N002"/>has your system to tell us, for religious education? This question has been answered by me,
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_2_tl_3" n="N003"/>and sometimes, as the educators told me, they accepted it, that the same structure which I use
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_2_tl_4" n="N004"/>in terms of existential questions and religious answers, answers in terms of religious symbols, also
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_2_tl_5" n="N005"/>must be used in alleducation—not only in the education of children in religion but in all education
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_2_tl_6" n="N006"/>which is more than a simplekanning of facts. Leerning of facts of course is necessary and is the
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_2_tl_7" n="N007"/>Bilderung
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_2_tl_8" n="N008"/>material with which everything else must be done, but education means more than this—and it certainly
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_2_tl_9" n="N009"/>does; even in humanism it means MüCH more than this —then I believe that this same method of
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_2_tl_10" n="N010"/>corixlation between question and answer can and must be applied to the (e-ducational problems
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_2_tl_11" n="N011"/>INALL realms, and including religious education.
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_2_tl_12" n="N012"/>Now what does this mean practically? It means that you listen to the actual questions
            </p>
            <p facs="#facs_79_tr_1">
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_1" n="N001"/>of the children, but many children will not ASK many ACTUAL questions, although those who ASK them
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_2" n="N002"/>are usually a little bit wiser than our great metaphysicians—they usually ask the same questions, only
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_3" n="N003"/>[correct?]
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_4" n="N004"/>in a little bit more
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_5" n="N005"/>and undistorted way. They areillely wiser than those who den
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_6" n="N006"/>dʼune manière vieuse
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_7" n="N007"/>dʼune manière beaucoup
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_8" n="N008"/>devenu
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_9" n="N009"/>dʼune manière
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_10" n="N010"/>toutes les
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_11" n="N011"/>ne se sont pas
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_12" n="N012"/>dʼun autre
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_13" n="N013"/>dʼune manière
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_14" n="N014"/>sont pas
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_15" n="N015"/>Pour Votre
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_16" n="N016"/>toutes
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_17" n="N017"/>dʼune manière
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_18" n="N018"/>qui me
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_19" n="N019"/>déciter les
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_20" n="N020"/>Vous avez
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_21" n="N021"/>Monsieur,
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_22" n="N022"/>Monsieur M r de
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_23" n="N023"/>dʼun autre
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_24" n="N024"/>dʼun autre
               <lb facs="#facs_79_tr_1_tl_25" n="N025"/>dʼune manière vieuse
            </p>
            
